Requirement was changed and now we want to enable PersonRepo class to hold both types Student and Staff. Provide a modified  implementation to reflect this change. 

public class PersonRepo{
public PersonRepo(){
  
    protected List<Student> students = new ArrayList<>(); 
  
    protected List<Staff> staffs = new ArrayList<>(); 
 
}
}


public class StudentRepo extends PersonRepo { 
 
 public void addStudent(Student s){ 
 students.add(s); 
 }


public class StaffRepo extends PersonRepo{ 
 public void addStaff(Staff s){ 
 staffs.add(s); 
 } 
